Day
  - 3 turns

Event Deck
  - 1 card played after player locks in turn decision
  - Changes outcome of turn slightly
Crew
  - Assign Crew to Duties
    - Mine
    - Food Production
    - Solar Energy Farm Operation
  - Can be injured (unusable for x turns)
  - Can be locked into duty for x turns (Research)
Stations
  => All un-upgrade stations follow rule: +1 max / person, +1 min / 2 people
  - Food Farm
    - 1 - 1 base / turn (0 people = 1 - 1, 1 people 1 - 2, 2 people 2 - 3, 3 people 2 - 4, etc)
  - Solar Farm
    - 1 - 1 base / turn (0 people = 1 - 1, 1 people 1 - 2, 2 people 2 - 3, 3 people 2 - 4, etc)
  - Asteroid Mine
    - 0 - 0 base (0 people = 0 - 0, 1 people 0 - 1, 2 people 1 - 2, 3 people 1 - 3, etc)
  - Research Lab
Upgrades
  - Cost Ore, Energy, and Man Power


Resources
  - Amounts also a range for the turn (ie. 1-3, 3-5)
  - Negative events can only reduce to the minimum minus 1
  - Positive Events are flat bonus on top of production (ie. +1 Energy, +2 Food)
Rations
  - Come from Hydroponic farm, can increase by manning it
  - Negative event spoil food, or reduce amount produced
  - Need 1 food / crew per day (3 turns)
Energy
  - Comes from Solar Farm passively, can increase by manning it
  - Negative Events reduce output for a turn
Ore
  - Comes from mining only when manned
  - Victory Points
  - Also used to repair damaged systems
  - Negative events can injured Crew Members for turn(s)



